ger-Verlag]]|year=2014|isbn=978-3-319-08816-7}} *{{cite book| editor1-last=Jeschke |editor1-first=Sabina |editor2-last=Kobbelt |editor2-first=Leif |editor3-last=Dröge |editor3-first=Alicia |title=Exploring Virtuality – Virtualität im interdisziplinären Diskurs |publisher=[[Springer Spektrum]]|year=2014|isbn=978-3-658-03885-4}} *{{cite book|title=Prethinking Work - Insights on the Future of Work 2011/2012|publisher=LIT|year=2012|isbn=978-3-643-90240-5|editor1-last=Jeschke|editor1-first=Sabina|editor2-last=Hees|editor2-first=Frank|editor3-last=Richert|editor3-first=Anja|editor4-last=Trantow|editor4-first=Sven}} *{{cite book| editor1-last=Jeschke | editor1-first=Sabina| editor2-last= Liu | editor2-first= Honghai | editor3-last= Schilberg | editor3-first= Daniel |title=Intelligent Robotics and Applications (Part I and II) |publisher=[[Springer-Verlag]]|year=2011}} {{ISBN|978-3-642-25486-4}}; {{ISBN|978-3-642-25489-5}} *{{cite book| editor1-last=Jeschke | editor1-first=Sabina| editor2-last=Isenhardt | editor2-first=Ingrid| editor3-last=Hees | editor3-first=Frank| editor4-last=Trantow | editor4-first=Sven |title=Enabling Innovation. Innovative Capability - German and International Views|publisher=[[Springer-Verlag]]|year=2011|isbn=978-3-642-24503-9|doi=10.1007/978-3-642-24503-9}}
